{"tid":1102394,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民建聯議員葛珮帆政府一定要收回這個醫生執業權，去引入海外，內地醫生香港係特區政府話事唔係班醫生","createTime":"2019-04-11T16:02:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-13T03:06:22.000Z","uid":125193,"like":2,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"305fd2b908b4d804948ec13c6cc2afe43d587ad7","tid":1102394,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T16:02:44.000Z","msg":"民建聯新界東議員葛珮帆指：「醫委會一而再、再而三，上一屆立法會提出(改革醫委會)，他們一個醫生就可『拉布』拉倒。政府要收回這個權，不可以再這樣下去，是我們市民生死大事，關乎你我的生命。負責的政府，你們說要新思維，拜託你們取回權力，由政府去決定如引入醫生，不可以再交給醫委會決定。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7TReUhb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7TReUhb.jpg&h=891d30d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h0NUUhc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh0NUUhc.jpg&h=db1a1488&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTVB <br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/5caf569de60383073220a54f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F5caf569de60383073220a54f&d=Cuyai%2BbkQ%2BZKjwazMoctzvo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=00288a40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/5caf569de60383073220a54f</a>"},{"pid":"5c558b06f7eb00fb6642639a0f4bee1f7479fb3d","tid":1102394,"uid":125193,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T16:03:36.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"d16e7f68554d833f640621ef4ed5a7a4ff471cce","tid":1102394,"uid":125193,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T16:06:02.000Z","msg":"將來引入大陸 doctor 我話 OK 就 OK"},{"pid":"5fde23ebb65658699632ddeee814dcbf32bce14b","tid":1102394,"uid":126510,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T16:07:45.000Z","msg":"葛博士假學歷單野點呀？<br />\n<br />\n佢好似依家改咗話自己係港大碩士<br />\n但佢申請港大碩士個陣用嘅學歷 唔係外國野雞嘅假學歷咩？<br />\n無得追究返？"},{"pid":"3f30ad278aa40b63f3cad59ef9cf9ccb1c6d46b3","tid":1102394,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-